text: Pennine may refer to: * Pennines, a mountain range in England * Pennine Alps, a mountain range in the western Alps * Pennine Way, a National Trail in England and Scotland * Pennine FM, an Independent Local Radio station in Huddersfield, West Yorkshire * Rolls-Royce Pennine, a British 46-litre air- cooled sleeve valve engine with 24 cylinders arranged in an X formation
title: Pennine
